						<summary>

						<p>On a slab lying in Survey No. 117.</p>						

						<p>Circa 17th century.</p>						

						<p>It speaks of the construction of a tank by several <hi rend="italic">Gauḍas</hi> and others. It also refers to a gift of land and house for the work. <hi rend="italic">Dēsāyi</hi> Nēmaṇa and <hi rend="italic">Dēsa-kulakarani</hi> Gōpaṇa are mentioned.</p>						

